      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im living in oslo and the sun is basically gone for like 4 months lol. i really want to maximize my immune system for the winter so i was thinking of doing a heavy vitamin d loading phase. is it actually okay to take like 50,000 iu every day for a few weeks just to get my levels up really fast? feels like it should work better than the tiny 1000 iu doses",
